| Type                         | Examples                                     | Can you create objects?                                          |
| ---------------------------- | -------------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------- |
| âœ… **Data Structure classes** | `ArrayList`, `HashMap`, `HashSet`, `TreeMap` | âœ”ï¸ YES â€” you can do `new ArrayList()`                            |
